Consult Your Doctor Before Use
Rem is an application helping you to track your sleep. You can improve your sleep routines by comparing your every night's history. The app can not diagnose, treat, cure, or stop any sleep disorders professionally so if you have chronic sleep concerns, consult with your doctor to go over possible reasons.
