Subscription
Rem users may access to the product in two ways:
Free Trial:
This plan gives unlimited access to all Rem features for 7 calendar days. You will not be charged if you cancel your subscription at least 24 hours before the end of the trial period.
Subscription:
This plan gives access to all Rem features while your subscription is active and it will renew automatically unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the current cycle ends. You can manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal in accounts setting.
The subscription plan is on monthly basis which constitutes 30 calendar days. For each month that your subscription is active, you permit Rem to charge the same price for the same plan as it used for the original subscription fee.
Your purchase will proceed through iTunes/App store and will be subject to Apple's applicable payment policy. Because the payments are handled by iTunes/App store, they can be refunded and approved only by Apple. To receive a refund you need to contact Apple directly.
Deleting the app dose not automatically cancel your subscription however You can turn off your subscription actively in your account setting of the app store. If you uninstall the app but don't cancel your subscription before it ends, you will still be charged.
